cs.SE, cs.PL, cs.LO, cs.CR, cs.AI. 

The paper presents a symbolic-execution-based algorithm for program analysis, which is a common topic in software engineering (cs.SE) and programming languages (cs.PL). The focus on necessary conditions suggests a connection to logic (cs.LO) and verification (cs.CR). The proposed application in bug-finding and test-generation also suggests a connection to artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
